        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3445614611" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6592528925986363394">Redeemed lawyer Zachary Black is back for his third outing, in &apos;Betrayal in Blue&apos; by Mark M. Bello. He has battled a corrupt church and white supremacy, but he might be facing his toughest challenge yet when an old foe Police Captain Jack Dylan is accused of murdering a terrorist. It&apos;s a race against the clock for Zach and his team investigators and scientists to locate the evidence that will exonerate Jack. Will Zach be able to work his magic in the courtroom for the third time or will Jack los</span>
  <span id="freeText6592528925986363394" style="display:none">Redeemed lawyer Zachary Black is back for his third outing, in 'Betrayal in Blue' by Mark M. Bello. He has battled a corrupt church and white supremacy, but he might be facing his toughest challenge yet when an old foe Police Captain Jack Dylan is accused of murdering a terrorist. It's a race against the clock for Zach and his team investigators and scientists to locate the evidence that will exonerate Jack. Will Zach be able to work his magic in the courtroom for the third time or will Jack lose his career, reputation, and freedom?<br /><br />It's another great courtroom thriller from Bello, with plenty of suspense, and again I read most of this book in a single sitting. Like his other novels, Bello creates a charged atmosphere and the plot really keeps you on your toes. I'm already onto book four, and I can't wait to read many more Zach Blake legal thrillers.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6592528925986363394" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


