  <span id="freeText4033903285511388978" style="display:none">This was such an exciting and tense crime novel, absolutely fantastic! The politics at play in this instalment makes for a great read and very informative coming from a former attorney. The storyline was well thought out and the characters are consistent and very interesting. The book brings a highly sensitive topic to the forefront and I'm addicted to these books. Bello continues to do a brilliant job with this series and I can't fault his style or storylines. I highly recommend the whole series if you haven't read the others yet. </span>
