<div id="review_2806644752" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2806644752" />
    <a title="Amie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/41406182-amie"><img alt="Amie" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2806644752?book_show_action=true">May 05, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amie" href="/user/show/41406182-amie">Amie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2806644752" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12281398058653193747"><strong>Fast paced crime novel</strong><br/><br/>Betrayal in Blue is a fast pace crime novel, the 3rd in the Zackary Blake series.  This series follows Dearborn, IL police captain Jack Dylan’s hunt for justice and Attorney Zachary Blake’s struggle to ensure that justice is enforced.  In this latest novel, Betrayal in Blue, Jack finds himself once again up against White Supremacist Terrorists as his team uncovers a plot to release a deadly attack on a Mosque in Dearborn.  Jack and his team strive to glean as much intel as </span>
  <span id="freeText12281398058653193747" style="display:none"><strong>Fast paced crime novel</strong><br /><br />Betrayal in Blue is a fast pace crime novel, the 3rd in the Zackary Blake series.  This series follows Dearborn, IL police captain Jack Dylan’s hunt for justice and Attorney Zachary Blake’s struggle to ensure that justice is enforced.  In this latest novel, Betrayal in Blue, Jack finds himself once again up against White Supremacist Terrorists as his team uncovers a plot to release a deadly attack on a Mosque in Dearborn.  Jack and his team strive to glean as much intel as they can before alerting the boys in the FBI and risking a hostile takeover of their investigation. Much to Jack’s unhappiness the FBI are soon on top of Jack’s team and when things go array during a take down of the supremacist group, the main player escapes into thin air. Jack takes it upon himself to right the wrong and searches out  the leader on his own. <br />Jack quickly finds the suspect and then finds himself accused of murder.   Indicted by a small town police chief, hell bent on making an example of Jack for his big  city bravado and lack of professional courtesy; things don’t look good for Jack. <br />Luckily Jack has distinguished defense attorney Zachary Blake in his back pocket. Will Blake be able to not just acquit his client of all charges but prove him innocent and save his career as a decorated law officer?<br /> Betray in Blue is an action packed novel full of suspense and unexpected twists.  Written like a true crime novel Betrayal in Blue has you feeling like you are part of the investigation team, privy to all the discoveries as they unfold. Well written, well plotted and leaving you loving the main players more and more, Betray in Blue earns a solid 4 stars.  <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="12281398058653193747" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


