  <span id="freeText1550815707971349386" style="display:none">I am giving this entire series five stars! After I read book 1, Betrayal of Faith, I bought the entire series knowing I would binge read it. Each book tackles a different social issue, this one is terrorism. <br />As in the author's previous books, I love the characters and plot. There is always plenty of action, drama, and suspense to keep the pages turning. <br />This series is well-written and engaging. I often find that there are books within a series that I find "weaker", or less entertaining, than the others, but that has not been the case the Zach Blake series. <br />I highly recommend this series!!</span>
